16 major tectonic plates.

71
00:03:12,384 --> 00:03:16,057
Tectonic plates are the outer-most layer of the Earth,

72
00:03:16,057 --> 00:03:18,711
made up of the Earth's crust 
and the upper part of the mantle.

73
00:03:18,711 --> 00:03:21,828
