238
00:09:48,757 --> 00:09:50,615
Second is the Seishin standard

239
00:09:50,615 --> 00:09:52,247
which is recommended for tall buildings

240
00:09:52,247 --> 00:09:54,226
where they are required to

241
00:09:54,226 --> 00:09:57,949
