242
00:09:58,520 --> 00:10:03,642
They need to put large, thick rubber mats 
under the foundation of the building.

243
00:10:03,916 --> 00:10:07,793
These rubber mats absorb the 
vibrations of earthquakes very well.

244
00:10:07,793 --> 00:10:11,085
But there is a third standard, 
which is even more strict,

245
00:10:11,085 --> 00:10:13,708
the most advanced standard,
the Menshin Standard.

246
00:10:14,142 --> 00:10:17,750
