building is isolated from the ground.

247
00:10:18,093 --> 00:10:20,593
Layers of lead, steel, and rubber are installed 

248
00:10:20,593 --> 00:10:24,341
so that the building moves independently of the ground.

249
00:10:24,341 --> 00:10:26,173
Even if the ground shakes, 
the building can remain stable.

