that spread over the Pacific Ocean.

292
00:12:19,230 --> 00:12:21,439
The 2011 earthquake and tsunami

293
00:12:21,439 --> 00:12:23,690
was the most devastating in Japan's history.

294
00:12:23,690 --> 00:12:26,391
Around 20,000 people lost their lives in it.

295
